{"id":185063,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011930/","date":"2011-10-01T01:00:32Z","modified":"2011-10-01T01:00:32Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/9/30","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a> <b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京烤鸭博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.pekingduck.org/2011/09/so-much-for-the-confucius-peace-prize/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“孔子和平奖”不过如此</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这个奖之所以会诞生，是因为刘晓波的获奖。媒体对这个奖的任何报道，都令人想起奥斯陆的空椅子。这大概是它被取消的根本原因。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/09/30/time-for-china-to-strike-back/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“中国到了该反击的时刻”</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——《环球时报》认为东南亚国家象蚊子一样，需要给它们一个教训。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/09/30/chinese-stocks-crushed-in-u-s-on-report-of-doj-probe/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美司法部调查中国公司的消息传出后，美国市场上的中国股大跌</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——优库跌幅最大，达</span></span><span><span>18%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，新浪、百度、搜狐等均有下跌。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社独家报道：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.boston.com/news/world/asia/articles/2011/09/30/ap_exclusive_us_scientist_trapped_in_china/?page=1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国科学家身陷中国</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——汽车尾气处理专家、美籍华人胡志成，因泄露商业机密被投入中国监狱，但出狱后依然无法离开中国</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnbc.com/id/44712011\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">重庆市长表示房地产税可以向全国推广</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——重庆已扩大了房地产税征收范围，同时市长表示，这个成功的示范可以明后年在全国推广</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-09-30/china-may-inject-cash-to-prevent-wenzhou-crisis-ing-says.html\">ING<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">称中国或许会注入资金防止温州民间借贷危机</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——全国地下借贷市场接近</span></span><span><span>4</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万亿元规模，可能比地方政府的债务问题更严重</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国国防部：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.defense.gov/pubs/pdfs/2011_cmpr_final.pdf\">2011<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年中国军力报告全文</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span></span><span><span>82</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">页</span></span><span><span>PDF</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">文件）</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/burmamyanmar/8798495/Burma-suspends-dam-project-after-rare-public-protest.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">缅甸政府搁置水坝建设项目</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——由于面对公众的反对，缅甸总统宣布停建靠近中缅边界，由中国援助的水坝项目</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110930/bs_nm/us_china_economy_hsbc_pmi\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国制造业连续三个月停滞，价格上升</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——世界经济不景气对中国有所影响，同时生产企业通胀在九月份加速，原材料价格上升。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">皮特森国际经济研究所：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.piie.com/blogs/china/?p=409&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+ChinaEconomicWatch+%28PIIE+China+Economic+Watch%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人民币成为自身成功的牺牲品</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——作为人民币海外市场的香港，在</span></span><span><span>13</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个月里人民币存款增长</span></span><span><span>535%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，但这对人民币今后走势的影响是好是坏还很难说</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/09/29/in-battle-to-save-chinese-its-test-vs-test/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">拯救中</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">文</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的战争：考试对撼</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国学生对英语的重视从托福热就能看得出来。教育部为了扭转这种重外语不重汉语的势头，开始设立新的汉语考试</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/09/29/landed-ladies-top-list-of-chinas-richest-women/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">胡润女富豪榜上，地产女商人名列前茅</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在胡润发布的中国女富豪榜上，前五名中有四名都是房地产商。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新西兰《新闻报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/the-press/news/5701545/Porn-issues-raised\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国留学生携带</span>10<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">盘色情卡通</span>DVD<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">进入新西兰，被警方起诉</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这位刚入学的新生，还没见到学校，就被机场警方给送上法院。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-4753955743918862489?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[9793,9041,15165]}